title: NYC Angels: Heiress's Baby Scandal
description: The socialite and the Texan doc-is this for real?After gossip headlines announce that reluctant socialite Eleanor Aston is in a "relationship" with smooth-talking Texan Tyler Donaldson, for one glorious night this fake fling becomes fact, not fiction! Devoted nurse Eleanor knows she's in over her head with neonatal doc Ty-and that's before the paparazzi discover her baby bombshell!
author: Janice Lynn
